TI  - PoseExaminer: Automated Testing of Out-of-Distribution Robustness in Human Pose and Shape Estimation
PY  - 2023
T2  - Proceedings of the IEEE Computer Society Conference on Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition
VL  - 2023-June
