AB  - Communication between humans and avatars will increase in the Metaverse, and the quality of that conversation will be important. Natural language communication of man-machine interface is a key technology. In addition, the Metaverse also requires automatic avatar responses that consider local content. In this research, we are developing a system that implements natural language processing using sentence transformers to achieve accurate local communication between humans and avatars in the Metaverse.  © 2023 IEEE.
