TI  - Mixed Reality Tabletop Gameplay: Social Interaction with a Virtual Human Capable of Physical Influence
PY  - 2021
T2  - IEEE Transactions on Visualization and Computer Graphics
VL  - 27
IS  - 8
C7  - 8936360
